"1 tablespoon Dijon mustard","2 teaspoons apple cider","3  (10-inch) flour tortillas","6 ounces Brie cheese, rind removed and cut into 1/4-inch-thick slices, divided","1  Fuji apple, cored and cut into 1/4-inch-thick slices (about 1/2 pound), divided","3 cups arugula, divided","3/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper, divided"